           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-acc-flg-exi      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-acc-cmp-exi-900.
       exe-acc-cmp-exi-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se uscita con Exit                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-acc-cmp-exi-900.
